{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":855,"text":"Two years ago, I set off\nfrom central London on the Tube"},{"time":4345,"text":"and ended up somewhere\nin the east of the city"},{"time":6667,"text":"walking into a self-storage unit"},{"time":8604,"text":"to meet a guy that had\n2,000 luxury polo shirts for sale."},{"time":13180,"text":"And as I made my way down the corridor,"},{"time":15129,"text":"a broken, blinking light made it\njust like the cliche scene"},{"time":18146,"text":"from a gangster movie."},{"time":20462,"text":"Our man was early,\nand he was waiting for me"},{"time":22668,"text":"in front of a unit secured\nwith four padlocks down the side."},{"time":26043,"text":"On our opening exchange,"},{"time":27604,"text":"it was like a verbal sparring match"},{"time":29367,"text":"where he threw the first punches."},{"time":31401,"text":"Who was I?\nDid I have a business card?"},{"time":33939,"text":"And where was I going to sell?"},{"time":35886,"text":"And then, he just started opening up,"},{"time":38590,"text":"and it was my turn."},{"time":40433,"text":"Where were the polo shirts coming from?"},{"time":42403,"text":"What paperwork did he have?"},{"time":44501,"text":"And when was his next shipment\ngoing to arrive?"},{"time":47056,"text":"I was treading the fine line"},{"time":48414,"text":"between asking enough questions\nto get what I needed"},{"time":51193,"text":"and not enough for him\nto become suspicious,"},{"time":53764,"text":"because what he didn't know\nis that I'm a counterfeit investigator,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":58318,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":59705,"text":"and after 20 minutes or so\nof checking over the product"},{"time":62492,"text":"for the telltale signs\nof counterfeit production --"},{"time":66031,"text":"say, badly stitched labels\nor how the packaging"},{"time":68381,"text":"had a huge brand logo\nstamped all over the front of it --"},{"time":71230,"text":"I was finally on my way out,"},{"time":73150,"text":"but not before he insisted\non walking down to the street with me"},{"time":76245,"text":"and back to the station."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79237,"text":"And the feeling after these meetings\nis always the same:"},{"time":81929,"text":"my heart is beating like a drum,"},{"time":84033,"text":"because you never know\nif they've actually bought your story,"},{"time":86952,"text":"or they're going to start following you\nto see who you really are."},{"time":90104,"text":"Relief only comes\nwhen you turn the first corner"},{"time":92478,"text":"and glance behind,\nand they're not standing there."},{"time":96171,"text":"But what our counterfeit\npolo shirt seller certainly didn't realize"},{"time":99376,"text":"is that everything I'd seen and heard\nwould result in a dawn raid on his house,"},{"time":103161,"text":"him being woken out of bed\nby eight men on his doorstep"},{"time":105972,"text":"and all his product seized."},{"time":108557,"text":"But this would reveal\nthat he was just a pawn"},{"time":112064,"text":"at the end of a counterfeiting network\nspanning three continents,"},{"time":115546,"text":"and he was just the first loose thread\nthat I'd started to pull on"},{"time":118688,"text":"in the hope that it would all unravel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":121697,"text":"Why go through all that trouble?"},{"time":124358,"text":"Well, maybe counterfeiting\nis a victimless crime?"},{"time":127365,"text":"These big companies,\nthey make enough money,"},{"time":129499,"text":"so if anything,"},{"time":130794,"text":"counterfeiting is just a free form\nof advertising, right?"},{"time":134170,"text":"And consumers believe just that --"},{"time":136570,"text":"that the buying and selling of fakes\nis not that big a deal."},{"time":140110,"text":"But I'm here to tell you\nthat that is just not true."},{"time":144848,"text":"What the tourist on holiday doesn't see\nabout those fake handbags"},{"time":148801,"text":"is they may well\nhave been stitched together"},{"time":151261,"text":"by a child who was trafficked\naway from her family,"},{"time":154774,"text":"and what the car repair shop\nowner doesn't realize"},{"time":157270,"text":"about those fake brake pads"},{"time":159427,"text":"is they may well be lining the pockets\nof an organized crime gang"},{"time":162793,"text":"involved in drugs and prostitution."},{"time":165950,"text":"And while those two things\nare horrible to think about,"},{"time":168864,"text":"it gets much worse,"},{"time":171196,"text":"because counterfeiting\nis even funding terrorism."},{"time":175043,"text":"Let that sink in for a moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177567,"text":"Terrorists are selling fakes\nto fund attacks,"},{"time":180420,"text":"attacks in our cities\nthat try to make victims of all of us."},{"time":185442,"text":"You wouldn't buy a live scorpion,"},{"time":187705,"text":"because there's a chance\nthat it would sting you on the way home,"},{"time":190777,"text":"but would you still buy a fake handbag"},{"time":192784,"text":"if you knew the profits\nwould enable someone to buy bullets"},{"time":196307,"text":"that would kill you and other\ninnocent people six months later?"},{"time":200594,"text":"Maybe not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202552,"text":"OK, time to come clean."},{"time":204668,"text":"In my youth --"},{"time":205843,"text":"yeah, I might look like I'm still\nclinging on to it a bit --"},{"time":208720,"text":"I bought fake watches\nwhile on holiday in the Canary Islands."},{"time":212395,"text":"But why do I tell you this?"},{"time":214229,"text":"Well, we've all done it,"},{"time":216705,"text":"or we know someone that's done it."},{"time":218404,"text":"And until this very moment,\nmaybe you didn't think twice about it,"},{"time":222071,"text":"and nor did I,"},{"time":223471,"text":"until I answered a 20-word cryptic advert"},{"time":226122,"text":"to become an intellectual\nproperty investigator."},{"time":230086,"text":"It said \"Full training given\nand some international travel.\""},{"time":233152,"text":"Within a week, I was creating\nmy first of many aliases,"},{"time":236925,"text":"and in the 10 years since,\nI've investigated fake car parts,"},{"time":240027,"text":"alloy wheels, fake pet grooming tools,"},{"time":243265,"text":"fake bicycle parts,"},{"time":244980,"text":"and, of course,\nthe counterfeiter's favorite,"},{"time":247131,"text":"fake luxury leather goods,\nclothing and shoes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251027,"text":"And what I've learned in the 10 years\nof investigating fakes"},{"time":253925,"text":"is that once you start\nto scratch the surface,"},{"time":256390,"text":"you find that they are rotten to the core,"},{"time":258576,"text":"as are the people and organizations\nthat are making money from them,"},{"time":263338,"text":"because they are profiting\non a massive, massive scale."},{"time":267499,"text":"You can only make\naround a hundred to 200 percent"},{"time":269952,"text":"selling drugs on the street."},{"time":271807,"text":"You can make 2,000 percent\nselling fakes online"},{"time":275674,"text":"with little of the same\nrisks or penalties."},{"time":278856,"text":"And this quick, easy money"},{"time":280165,"text":"then goes on to fund\nthe more serious types of crime,"},{"time":282833,"text":"and it pays the way\nto making these organizations,"},{"time":285421,"text":"these criminal organizations,\nlook more legitimate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":288863,"text":"So let me bring you in on a live case."},{"time":291620,"text":"Earlier this year,\na series of raids took place"},{"time":293843,"text":"in one of my longest-running\ninvestigations."},{"time":296470,"text":"Five warehouses were raided in Turkey,"},{"time":299547,"text":"and over two million finished\ncounterfeit clothing products were seized,"},{"time":303384,"text":"and it took 16 trucks\nto take that all away."},{"time":307288,"text":"But this gang had been clever."},{"time":308742,"text":"They had gone to the lengths\nof creating their own fashion brands,"},{"time":312154,"text":"complete with registered trademarks,"},{"time":314161,"text":"and even having photo shoots\non yachts in Italy."},{"time":319124,"text":"And they would use these completely\nunheard-of and unsuspicious brand names"},{"time":322806,"text":"as a way of shipping\ncontainer loads of fakes"},{"time":325472,"text":"to shell companies\nthat they'd set up across Europe."},{"time":328974,"text":"And documents found during those raids"},{"time":330870,"text":"found that they'd been falsifying\nshipping documents"},{"time":334268,"text":"so the customs officials\nwould literally have no idea"},{"time":337038,"text":"who had sent the products\nin the first place."},{"time":339944,"text":"When police got access\nto just one bank account,"},{"time":342325,"text":"they found nearly three million euros"},{"time":344163,"text":"had been laundered out of Spain\nin less than two years,"},{"time":347632,"text":"and just two days after those raids,"},{"time":349735,"text":"that gang were trying to bribe a law firm\nto get their stock back."},{"time":354782,"text":"Even now, we have no idea\nwhere all that money went,"},{"time":357870,"text":"to who it went to,"},{"time":359060,"text":"but you can bet it's never going\nto benefit the likes of you or me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":363970,"text":"But these aren't just\nlow-level street thugs."},{"time":366739,"text":"They're business professionals,\nand they fly first class."},{"time":369900,"text":"They trick legitimate businesses"},{"time":371830,"text":"with convincing fake invoices\nand paperwork,"},{"time":374814,"text":"so everything just seems real,"},{"time":376464,"text":"and then they set up eBay\nand Amazon accounts"},{"time":379084,"text":"just to compete with the people\nthey've already sold fakes to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":383813,"text":"But this isn't just happening online."},{"time":386117,"text":"For a few years, I also used to attend\nautomotive trade shows"},{"time":390618,"text":"taking place in huge exhibition spaces,"},{"time":393325,"text":"but away from the Ferraris\nand the Bentleys and the flashing lights,"},{"time":396541,"text":"there'd be companies selling fakes:"},{"time":398499,"text":"companies with a brochure on the counter"},{"time":401214,"text":"and another one underneath,\nif you ask them the right questions."},{"time":404540,"text":"And they would sell me fake car parts,\nfaulty fake car parts"},{"time":407375,"text":"that have been estimated to cause\nover 36,000 fatalities,"},{"time":411916,"text":"deaths on our roads each year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":415182,"text":"Counterfeiting is set to become\na 2.3-trillion-dollar underground economy,"},{"time":421095,"text":"and the damage that can be done\nwith that kind of money,"},{"time":424174,"text":"it's really frightening ..."},{"time":426587,"text":"because fakes fund terror."},{"time":429929,"text":"Fake trainers on the streets of Paris,"},{"time":432374,"text":"fake cigarettes in West Africa,"},{"time":434841,"text":"and pirate music CDs in the USA"},{"time":437080,"text":"have all gone on to fund\ntrips to training camps,"},{"time":440358,"text":"bought weapons and ammunition,\nor the ingredients for explosives."},{"time":444421,"text":"In June 2014, the French security services"},{"time":447644,"text":"stopped monitoring the communications\nof Said and Cherif Kouachi,"},{"time":453644,"text":"the two brothers who had been\non a terror watch list for three years."},{"time":457548,"text":"But that summer, they were only\npicking up that Cherif was buying"},{"time":460796,"text":"fake trainers from China,"},{"time":462879,"text":"so it signaled a shift away from extremism"},{"time":465538,"text":"into what was considered\na low-level petty crime."},{"time":469752,"text":"The threat had gone away."},{"time":472049,"text":"Seven months later,"},{"time":473231,"text":"the two brothers walked into the offices\nof Charlie Hebdo magazine"},{"time":476413,"text":"and killed 12 people, wounded 11 more,"},{"time":479242,"text":"with guns from the proceeds\nof those fakes."},{"time":482603,"text":"So whatever you think, this isn't\na faraway problem happening in China."},{"time":486259,"text":"It's happening right here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":489528,"text":"And Paris is not unique."},{"time":491642,"text":"Ten years earlier, in 2004,\n191 people lost their lives"},{"time":495778,"text":"when a Madrid commuter train was bombed."},{"time":498307,"text":"The attack had been partly funded\nby the sale of pirate music CDs in the US."},{"time":502880,"text":"Two years prior to that,\nan Al Qaeda training manual"},{"time":505746,"text":"recommended explicitly selling fakes"},{"time":508340,"text":"as a good way of supporting terror cells."}]},{"cues":[{"time":512574,"text":"But despite this, despite the evidence\nconnecting terrorism and counterfeiting,"},{"time":517733,"text":"we do go on buying them,\nincreasing the demand"},{"time":520527,"text":"to the point where\nthere's even a store in Turkey"},{"time":522900,"text":"called \"I Love Genuine Fakes.\""},{"time":526688,"text":"And you have tourists posing\nwith photographs on TripAdvisor,"},{"time":529911,"text":"giving it five-star reviews."},{"time":532301,"text":"But would those same tourists\nhave gone into a store"},{"time":534760,"text":"called \"I Love Genuine Fake Viagra Pills\""},{"time":538096,"text":"or \"I Genuinely Love Funding Terrorism\"?"},{"time":541282,"text":"I doubt it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":543564,"text":"Many of us think\nthat we're completely helpless"},{"time":546534,"text":"against organized crime and terrorism,"},{"time":548644,"text":"that we can do nothing\nabout the next attack,"},{"time":551574,"text":"but I believe you can."},{"time":553755,"text":"You can by becoming investigators, too."},{"time":557875,"text":"The way we cripple these networks\nis to cut their funding,"},{"time":560780,"text":"and that means cutting the demand"},{"time":562416,"text":"and changing this idea\nthat it's a victimless crime."},{"time":565197,"text":"Let's all identify counterfeiters,"},{"time":567682,"text":"and don't give them our money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":569736,"text":"So here's a few tips\nfrom one investigator to another"},{"time":572420,"text":"to get you started."},{"time":574633,"text":"Number one:"},{"time":575934,"text":"here's a typical\nonline counterfeiter's website."},{"time":579263,"text":"Note the URL."},{"time":580923,"text":"If you're shopping for sunglasses\nor camera lenses, say,"},{"time":583908,"text":"and you come across a website\nlike medical-insurance-bankruptcy.com,"},{"time":587438,"text":"start to get very suspicious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589027,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":590577,"text":"Counterfeiters register\nexpired domain names"},{"time":592873,"text":"as a way of keeping up\nthe old website's Google page ranking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597401,"text":"Number two:"},{"time":598576,"text":"is the website screaming at you\nthat everything is 100 percent genuine,"},{"time":602083,"text":"but still giving you 75 percent\noff the latest collection?"},{"time":606003,"text":"Look for words like \"master copy,\""},{"time":608455,"text":"\"overruns,\" \"straight from the factory.\""},{"time":611201,"text":"They could write this all in Comic Sans,\nit's that much of a joke."}]},{"cues":[{"time":614345,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":615978,"text":"Number three:"},{"time":617236,"text":"if you get as far as the checkout page,"},{"time":619136,"text":"and you don't see \"https\"\nor a padlock symbol next to the URL,"},{"time":624423,"text":"you should really start thinking\nabout closing the tab,"},{"time":627059,"text":"because these indicate\nactive security measures"},{"time":629361,"text":"that will keep your personal\nand credit card information safe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":632490,"text":"OK, last one:"},{"time":634607,"text":"go hunting for the \"Contact Us\" page."},{"time":636835,"text":"If you can only find a generic webform,"},{"time":639688,"text":"no company name, telephone number,\nemail address, postal address --"},{"time":643637,"text":"that's it, case closed."},{"time":645721,"text":"You found a counterfeiter."},{"time":647992,"text":"Sadly, you're going to have\nto go back to Google"},{"time":650287,"text":"and start your shopping search\nall over again,"},{"time":652455,"text":"but you didn't get ripped off,\nso that's only a good thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":656601,"text":"As the world's most famous\nfictional detective would say,"},{"time":660197,"text":"\"Watson, the game is afoot.\""},{"time":663027,"text":"Only this time, my investigator friends,"},{"time":665582,"text":"the game is painfully real."}]},{"cues":[{"time":667973,"text":"So the next time you're shopping online,"},{"time":670099,"text":"or perhaps wherever it is,"},{"time":672020,"text":"look closer, question a little bit\ndeeper, and ask yourself --"},{"time":676236,"text":"before you hand over\nthe cash or click \"Buy,\""},{"time":679171,"text":"\"Am I sure this is real?\""},{"time":681208,"text":"Tell your friend that used to buy\ncounterfeit watches"},{"time":684682,"text":"that he may just have brought\nthe next attack one day closer."},{"time":688335,"text":"And, if you see\nan Instagram advert for fakes,"},{"time":690834,"text":"don't keep scrolling past,"},{"time":692248,"text":"report it to the platform as a scam."}]},{"cues":[{"time":695375,"text":"Let's shine a light\non the dark forces of counterfeiting"},{"time":698461,"text":"that are hiding in plain sight."},{"time":700460,"text":"So please, spread the word"},{"time":702549,"text":"and don't stop investigating."}]},{"cues":[{"time":704385,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":705560,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}